---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow hero-eyebrow">GOOGLE PLAY SUBMISSION SERVICE</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Your app is built. We get it past Google's review gauntlet.</h1>
    <p class="hero-subhead">Submission, policy compliance, and rejection recovery for React Native, Expo, and Android apps. Live in 7 days or full refund on the Express tier.</p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="#intake" data-gc-event="cta-get-my-app-live" data-gc-title="CTA: Get my app live">Get my app live</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="#pricing" data-gc-event="cta-see-pricing" data-gc-title="CTA: See pricing">See pricing</a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-trust mono">Built by the dev behind stockportfolio.pro · 5 apps shipped to Google Play in 6 months · Taking 3 clients this week</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-block: 120px 100px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    color: var(--approved);
  }

  .hero-title {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .hero-subhead {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--cta);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: none;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background-color 150ms ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--cta-hover);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    padding: 14px 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: border-color 150ms ease, background-color 150ms ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--soft);
  }

  .hero-trust {
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding-block: 80px 60px;
    }

    .hero-subhead {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
